Package de.weltraumschaf.ebnf.parser

Parser package.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Parser Parses a stream of EBNF tokens and generate a abstract syntax tree.
Position Represents a token position in the source string.
Scanner Scans an input string for EBNF syntax tokens.
Token Represents a scanned EBNF token with its type, value and position in the source file.
 

Enum Summary
TokenType Defines all token types.
 

Exception Summary
SyntaxException Exception for signaling syntax errors.
 

Package de.weltraumschaf.ebnf.parser Description

Parser package.

Contains everything necessary to parse EBN syntax.

This package is a part of the open-source EBNF library
